i just don't understand you!

05:19.167 --> 05:23.207
One minute you want to make love to me,
the next you don't even notice I'm there!

05:23.333 --> 05:24.923
Sometimes you scare me.

05:25.042 --> 05:27.132
It's not me that scares you.

05:28.583 --> 05:30.423
