10:34.042 --> 10:36.542
- No, thank you.
- Please!

10:36.625 --> 10:38.245
- No!
- I insist.

10:38.375 --> 10:41.705
- You must take it.
- Get out! Get out! All of you!

10:44.708 --> 10:47.118
