12:00.667 --> 12:03.917
Oh, tom. Tom!

12:04.917 --> 12:07.127
You're up to something, aren't you?

12:10.000 --> 12:12.080
Everybody dies, don't they?

12:12.208 --> 12:14.248
But some come back.

12:15.333 --> 12:16.713
Isn't that so?

12:16.833 --> 12:19.583
You tried to get into
the locked room today, didn't you?

12:19.708 --> 12:23.418
How do the dead come back, mother?
What's the secret?

12:25.208 --> 12:28.828
Oh, tom, don't go on with this.

12:28.958 --> 12:31.038
You don't know enough.

12:31.167 --> 12:35.127
That room's been locked for 18 years.

12:35.250 --> 12:38.170
And my father's been dead for 18 years.

12:38.292 --> 12:41.252
You know why the fuzz called, mother?

12:42.917 --> 12:44.917
We blew a fellow's mind.

12:45.042 --> 12:46.882
It was beautiful.

12:47.000 --> 12:48.880
Should've been there.

12:49.000 --> 12:51.420
He went right through the windscreen.

12:52.292 --> 12:55.332
It was great fun.

12:55.458 --> 12:59.078
But just you wait till you hear what
we've got planned for tomorrow night.

12:59.208 --> 13:01.208
You're threatening me, aren't you?

13:01.333 --> 13:05.213
