13:15.417 --> 13:17.827
That room could destroy him.

13:17.958 --> 13:20.078
Not with this protection.

13:28.375 --> 13:31.745
- Will the room give me the secret?
- It may.

13:33.333 --> 13:35.373
It depends on you.

13:36.375 --> 13:37.875
On what you are.

13:38.000 --> 13:41.710
If you're afraid,
we won't think any less of you.

13:51.417 --> 13:53.627
I'm not chickening out, shadwell.

15:29.958 --> 15:32.038
Shadwell!

15:33.083 --> 15:34.673
Mother!

20:15.708 --> 20:18.578
Oh! My poor boy!

20:19.500 --> 20:22.670
