that you're going to come back.

21:02.917 --> 21:06.627
"You've got to believe that
with all your being."

21:06.750 --> 21:08.170
Thank you, mother.

21:09.458 --> 21:11.918
Thank you very much.

21:46.833 --> 21:49.293
